Key.Chinesesimp:
Use: 与要访问其负载的单元同步.
Function: 如果它与单个单元同步，你可以通过AddAction来装备它的负载，它将出现在第一个同步单元中(在你只与一个对象同步的情况下)，或者在第二个同步对象中(在你首先同步了单元，然后与对象同步的情况下)..
Key.Original:
Use: Synchronize with the unit to which you want to access its loadout.
Function: If it is synchronized with a single unit, you can equip its loadout by means of an AddAction that will appear in the first synchronized unit (in the case that you have only synchronized with one object) or in the second synchronized object (in the case that you have synchronized first the unit and then with an object).
Key.English:
Use: Synchronize with the unit to which you want to access its loadout.
Function: If it is synchronized with a single unit, you can equip its loadout by means of an AddAction that will appear in the first synchronized unit (in the case that you have only synchronized with one object) or in the second synchronized object (in the case that you have synchronized first the unit and then with an object). TFAR mod compatible.
Key.Spanish:
Uso: Sincroniza con la unidad a la que quieres acceder a su loadout.
Función: Si se sincroniza con una sola unidad puedes equiparte su loadout mediante un AddAction que aparecera en la primeara unidad sicronizada (en el caso de que solo hayas sincronizado con un objeto) o en el segundo objeto sincronizado (en el caso de que hayas sincronizado primero la unidad y después con un objeto).

Key.Chinesesimp:
例子: 需要创建2 虚拟的情况
车库:
- 将虚拟车库模块与2个对象(to)同步让他们进入虚拟车库.
- 创建一个空标记(使用地图视图),其中将出现载具.
- 我们给每个空标记一个名称(在本例中:VGmarker_X).
- 我建议你使用一些直升机停机坪,伞兵信号或其他一些东西的目的指示将出现载具的区域.
- 车库列表:['VGmarker_0','VGmarker_1'].
Key.Original:
Example: Case in which do you want to create 2 Virtual Garages:
- Synchronize the Virtual Garage module with 2 objects (to give them acces to Virtual Garage).
- Creat an empty marker (using the map view) where the vehícle will appear.
- We give to each empty markers a name (in the example: VGmarker_X).
- I recomend you to use some helipad, paratrooper signal or some other thing with the purposeto of indicating the zone where the vheícle will appear.
- Garage List: ['VGmarker_0','VGmarker_1'].
Key.English:
Example: Case in which do you want to create 2 Virtual Garages:
- Synchronize the Virtual Garage module with 2 objects (to give them acces to Virtual Garage).
- Creat an empty marker (using the map view) where the vehícle will appear.
- We give to each empty markers a name (in the example: VGmarker_X).
- I recomend you to use some helipad, paratrooper signal or some other thing with the purposeto of indicating the zone where the vheícle will appear.
- Garage List: ['VGmarker_0','VGmarker_1'].
Key.Spanish:
Ejemplo: Caso en el que se quiere colocar 2 garajes:
- Sincronizar el modulo de Garaje Virtual con dos objetos (para darles acceso al Garaje Virtual).
- Crear un marcador Vacio en cada zona que queremos que aparezca el vehículo (desde el mapa).
- A cada marcador le ponemos un nombre (in this example: VGmarker_X).
- Recomiendo poner un helipuerto, se?alicación de paracaidista o se?al, de que allí aparecera el vehículo.
- Lista de Garajes: ['VGmarker_0','VGmarker_1'].
